<h2 data-nh-numbering="1.2. ">Pre-Requisites</h2>
<p>To login as an agent, we should have Sandbox access for the required test environment. We have two types of Agents L1 &amp; L2. L1 Agent can login to the Sandbox URL and create a Return Request for Stock Rotation. L2 Agent can view the cases assigned to them and can change the case owner. This page will only pertain to L1 agent.</p>
<p>
  <strong>Sandbox (IAOQA) Link :</strong> <a href="https://isvc--isvciaoqa.sandbox.my.salesforce.com/">https://isvc--isvciaoqa.sandbox.my.salesforce.com/</a>
</p>
<p>Access related issues, Contact: @Indus ISVC GRL R4C  </p>
