  </ac:image>
</p>
<ul>
  <li>We are checking <a href="#handytip-7173911966147491">ECB</a> Block only for the Sold to <a href="#handytip-3292677441675843">CMF</a> level Account.<ac:structured-macro ac:macro-id="bff7d467-1f2a-4d47-ae7f-052fb8ab8a98" ac:name="handy-tip" ac:schema-version="1">
      <ac:parameter ac:name="id">3292677441675843</ac:parameter>
      <ac:parameter ac:name="atlassian-macro-output-type">INLINE</ac:parameter>
      <ac:rich-text-body>
