<h3 data-nh-numbering="1.9.6. ">Product Validation/PO History</h3>
<p>
  <span style="color:var(--ds-background-accent-red-subtle,#f87168);">#NCNR is not mentioned here go through the code and add those validations here</span>
</p>
<p>
  <ac:image>
    <ri:attachment ri:filename="image-2026-7-6_11-20-13.png"/>
  </ac:image>
</p>
<ul>
  <li>On click of the PO History Button, we will be performing a POH API callout to get the PO numbers by sending the parameters MMs, Active CMFs of the bag, Start date, End date, sales org, Disti channel</li>
  <li>While validating from POH API initially the data range would be Current date -- 5 years. </li>
  <li>If we get the PO numbers for all the required line items, agent can directly proceed further.</li>
  <li>If we don't get the PO numbers for all the selected line items, we will show an error toast message.</li>
  <li>We do an additional validation check after the PO history check is done; this is done for each line item individually.</li>
  <li>Using the line item details, we query the 'NPR rule matrix records' and if the corresponding matrix record is found, then the line item is validated.</li>
  <li>If the validation fails, the line item is disabled, and the customer is shown the validation error message 'This product is not eligible for this return reason'.</li>
  <li>Agent can proceed to the next step by clicking on 'Next'. Agent would be navigated to the 'Credit Price validation screen'.</li>
</ul>
<p>
  <ac:image>
    <ri:attachment ri:filename="image-2026-7-6_11-20-25.png"/>
  </ac:image>
</p>
